cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "SEA:CUT / Friendly Floaty — open-source river-to-sea litter drifter"
message: "If you use this design, firmware, docs, or data, please cite it. Cite observation data by its obs_id (and by DOI once a dataset is deposited)."
type: software
authors:
  - name: "사단법인 이타서울 (Itaseoul) / GAA (Global Adopt-a-Beach Alliance) and contributors"
repository-code: "https://github.com/Itaseoul/seacut"
url: "https://github.com/Itaseoul/seacut"
license:
